files.Title: Dnn.PersonaBar.Library.AppEvents.Attributes.IgnoreVersionMatchCheckAttribute
files.Summary: Attribute to be used to decorate IAppLifecycleEvent implementors. This will ignore the version match check that is performed to avoid load IAppLifecycleEvent implementors on assembly with a version different from the version of Dnn.PersonaBar.Library.

files.Title: Dnn.PersonaBar.Library.AppEvents.IAppEvents
files.Summary: This interface defines methods that need to be called at various points during the application lifecycle. All modules that need to have any housekeeping applied during these events, need to create a concrete class that extends this interface. The main application start event will enumerate these (through reflection) and call the related methods in these classes.
